{"id":275263,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-杭州异议人士吕耿松外出会友被贴身跟踪/","date":"2013-01-19T07:16:09Z","modified":"2013-01-19T07:16:09Z","title":"维权网 | 杭州异议人士吕耿松外出会友被贴身跟踪","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员亦然报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日上午</span><span>，杭州异议人士吕耿松外出会友时，发现被由辖区派出所安排的一名协警贴身跟踪。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>杭州民主人士公开声援南方周末，要求言论自由后，吕耿松被抄家，毛庆祥、吕耿松、任伟仁、楼保生、王向晨、邹巍、戚惠民、陈树庆等人都陆续遭到传唤。随后，杭州大多数异议人士都被软禁在家中无法自由出行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>吕耿松：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1983</span><span>年毕业于杭州大学历史系，曾在浙江高等公安专科学校任教，因为支持民主运动而在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1993</span><span>年被开除公职后，成为自由撰稿人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2008</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>被杭州市中级法院以</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>煽动颠覆国家政权罪</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>判处有期徒刑四年，剥夺政治权利一年。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>吕耿松刑满出狱后，一直坚持民主宪政的探索和维权之路，因此多次遭到传唤、抄家，长期受到监控。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,9282,19196]}